Snowman ring is an untradeable cosmetic holiday item. A snowman ring can be obtained by completing one of the Christmas holiday events from 2021 onwards. When equipped, players are given the option to transform into three different types of snowmen: Traditional, Tempy, or Thermy.

When equipped, players are given the option to transform into three different types of snowmen: Traditional, Tempy, or Thermy.
